OL,7,F"Scammers are obtaining people's data
OL,8,Fthrough the dark web and then using it
OL,9,Fto get through the phone companies'
OL,10,Fsystems because they have the full
OL,11,Fbody of data that a company would
OL,12,Fexpect."
OL,14,FThere are fears that the growth in the
OL,15,FeSim, which effectively removes the
OL,16,Fneed for a physical simcard will make
OL,17,Fsim swap fraud easier to carry out.
OL,19,FHow does a SIM swap scam work?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
