OL,7,FThey will also be able to benefit from
OL,8,Fthe victim trying to access their
OL,9,Faccounts when they realise something
OL,10,Fis wrong because they will be pushed a
OL,11,Ftwo-factor login code that will be
OL,12,Fsent straight to the scammer.
OL,14,FIan Finlay said he was on a cruise
OL,15,Fnear Australia, and noticed something
OL,16,Fwas wrong when his credit card was
OL,17,Fdeclined during one of the port stops.
