OL,7,FHe told ITV's This Morning, he assumed
OL,8,Fit was a glitch, but then soon noticed
OL,9,Fsome transactions on his current
OL,10,Faccount that he had not authorised.
OL,12,FHe noticed fraudsters were paying for
OL,13,Fmeals on his credit card and booked a
OL,14,Fholiday to New York on his current
OL,15,Faccount.
OL,17,FWhen Mr Finlay got home, he realised
OL,18,Fit was "something bigger" than a card
OL,19,Fscam and all of his finances had been
OL,20,Faffected with his savings account also
OL,21,Fraided.
