OL,7,FEventually, he realised that combining
OL,8,Fthe money spent in his name and money
OL,9,Fremoved from his accounts totalled
OL,10,Faround #50,000.
OL,12,FWhen he was asking "what I had done
OL,13,Fwrong" he realised he had done nothing
OL,14,Fwrong, he said: "Your mobile phone
OL,15,Fcompany has sent a duplicate sim to an
OL,16,Faddress not connected to your account
OL,17,Fthat somebody has put in a phone and
OL,18,Fthen they've got everything they need
OL,19,Fto know about you."
