OL,7,FHe added: "The added implication is
OL,8,Fthat we are now also pushed into two-
OL,9,Fstage authentication. I was sat trying
OL,10,Fto look at my accounts, trying to get
OL,11,Finto them, getting a message saying
OL,12,Fwe'll forward you a code.
OL,14,F"That never arrived, I now know that
OL,15,Fwas being skimmed off by the scammer,
OL,16,Fthey were then using it to get into my
OL,17,Faccount and do even more damage."
OL,19,FHow can you protect yourself against
OL,20,Fsim-swap fraud?
