OL,7,FThere are several things you can do to
OL,8,Favoid being the victim of sim-swap
OL,9,Ffraud.
OL,11,FConsumer magazine Which? Has five
OL,12,Ftips. First, secure your mobile
OL,13,Faccount.
OL,15,FAsk your provider about any extra
OL,16,Fsecurity that can be added to the
OL,17,Faccount, like unique pins or
OL,18,Fauthenticator apps that can be added
OL,19,Fon top of standard password
OL,20,Fverification.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
