OL,7,FFor the fraud to work, the criminal
OL,8,Fneeds access to enough data to
OL,9,Fconvince a mobile carrier they are you.
OL,11,FInformation like place and date of
OL,12,Fbirth is often used as security
OL,13,Fquestions and should not be visible on
OL,14,Fsocial media profiles.
OL,16,FFourth, if you ever receive
OL,17,Finformation about your sim being
OL,18,Fchanged or you unexpectedly lose phone
OL,19,Fservice, contact your carrier
OL,20,Fimmediately.
